abstract: College Basketball Men's Roundup; University of Iowa beats Michigan State, 83-70; other scores noted.
lead_paragraph: The Hawkeyes led by as many as 19 points against the visiting Spartans and were led by Mike Gesell, who scored a career-high 25.

headline.main: Iowa Knocks No. 1 Michigan State From Ranks of the Unbeaten
